headline: Nasdaq Halts Empro Group Inc.
summary: NEW YORK, Oct. 23, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- The Nasdaq Stock Market® (Nasdaq: NDAQ) announced that trading is halted in Empro Group Inc. (Nasdaq: EMPG) for additional information requested from the company. Previously, the Securities and Exchange Commission effected a trading suspension in EMPG from 04:00:00 on October 9, 2025 to 23:59:00 on October 22, 2025. The last sale price of the company’s ordinary shares was $17.36. More information about the SEC’s order can be found at https://www.sec.go
